{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And so this was going on until the establishment of the state of Israel.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I met, in the meantime, my wife.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was Italian citizen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she was a doctor, a medical doctor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She practiced dentistry because in Italy, there is no special school for dentistry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You get a medical degree and-- because her first husband was a dentist, also.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was Italian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Janet.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] since she was a-- she had very good connections in Italy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the Gasperi's daughter, daughter-- the Gasperi was the prime minister.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His daughter was a-- we had a connection.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Through her, we arranged all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And through her, we got very good connection with the Italian authorities.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we could do a lot of things in Italy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and after the establishment of the state, since I had all the connections with the authorities, everybody left-- many, most of them left for Israel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I still had to liquidate everything, which was-- you know, we couldn't just pick ourselves.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was-- people were involved, Italian citizens, Jewish-Italian citizens, lawyers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Also, we arranged all kind of passports we could get for the-- if the Joint Distribution wanted to send people to South America, there were, at that time, Nelson Passports.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I could get them from the government because I had the connections with the Italian ministry, internal ministry, foreign ministry.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I was supposed to stay a little while longer.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
